# Checked-in test fixtures under tests/golden/ are inputs (sample CC5X .occ/.var/.fcs
# reports the parsers run against), NOT build artifacts -- never let the *.occ/*.var/etc.
# rules above ignore them, or CI checks out a tree without them and test_measure fails.
!tests/golden/**
